parameters.name: R
parameters.description: Radial distance of spacecraft from Saturn (Radius of Saturn).

parameters.name: RHO
parameters.description: Spacecraft position angle rho (radians).

parameters.name: BRHO
parameters.description: Rho component of the magnetic field (nanoTesla).

parameters.name: BPHI
parameters.description: Phi component of the magnetic field (nanoTesla).

parameters.name: BZ
parameters.description: Z component of the magnetic field (nanoTesla).

parameters.name: MODE
parameters.description: Instrument mode (l or m).

parameters.name: FDATE
parameters.description: Date the fit was performed (MMDDYY).

parameters.name: WHO
parameters.description: Initials of person who performed fit (JDR  = Dr. John Richardson, MIT).

parameters.name: CHI2
parameters.description: Chi-square of the fit.

parameters.name: NUM_FIT
parameters.description: Number of the ion species for the fit.

parameters.name: IONSPEC1
parameters.description: Atomic number of the first ion species for the fit.

parameters.name: IONMASS1
parameters.description: Mass of the first ion species for the fit.

parameters.name: IONCHRG1
parameters.description: Charge of the first ion species for the fit.

parameters.name: DEN1
parameters.description: Density of the first ion species.

parameters.name: XDEN1
parameters.description: Standard deviation for the density of the first ion species.

parameters.name: VRHO1
parameters.description: Rho component of the velocity vector for the first ion species.

parameters.name: XVRHO1
parameters.description:
Standard deviation for the rho component of the velocity vector for     
                        the first ion species.

parameters.name: VPHI1
parameters.description: Phi component of the velocity vector for the first ion species.

parameters.name: XVPHI1
parameters.description:
Standard deviation for for phi component of the velocity vector for     
                        the first ion species.

parameters.name: VZ1
parameters.description: Z component of the velocity vector for the first ion species.

parameters.name: XVZ1
parameters.description:
Standard deviation for the Z component of the velocity vector for the   
                        first ion species.

parameters.name: WPAR1
parameters.description: Thermal speed in parallel direction.

parameters.name: XWPAR1
parameters.description: Standard deviation for the thermal speed in parallel direction.

parameters.name: WPER1
parameters.description: Thermal speed in perpendicular direction.

parameters.name: XWPER1
parameters.description: Standard deviation for the thermal speed in perpendicular direction.

parameters.name: IONSPEC2
parameters.description: Atomic number of the second ion species for the fit.

parameters.name: IONMASS2
parameters.description: Mass of the second ion species for the fit.

parameters.name: IONCHRG2
parameters.description: Charge of the second ion species for the fit.

parameters.name: DEN2
parameters.description: Density of the second ion species.

parameters.name: XDEN2
parameters.description: Standard deviation for the density of the second ion species.

parameters.name: VRHO2
parameters.description: Rho component of the velocity vector for the second ion species.

parameters.name: XVRHO2
parameters.description:
Standard deviation for the rho component of the velocity vector for     
                        the second ion species.

parameters.name: VPHI2
parameters.description: Phi component of the velocity vector for the second ion species.

parameters.name: XVPHI2
parameters.description:
Standard deviation for the phi component of the velocity vector for     
                        the second ion species.

parameters.name: VZ2
parameters.description: Z component of the velocity vector for the second ion species.

parameters.name: XVZ2
parameters.description:
Standard deviation for the z component of the velocity vector for       
                        the second ion species.

parameters.name: WPAR2
parameters.description: Thermal speed in parallel direction.

parameters.name: XWPAR2
parameters.description: Standard deviation for the thermal speed in parallel direction.

parameters.name: WPER2
parameters.description: Thermal speed in perpendicular direction.

parameters.description: Standard deviation for the thermal speed in perpendicular direction.
